<project name="home:ciriarte:pve-HitachiBlockPlugin">
  <title>Proxmox VE storage plugin for Hitachi block storage (ALPHA)</title>
  <description>
    Storage plugin for Proxmox VE that integrates with Hitachi FC-based block
    storage (VSP One Block, VSP E series, VSP G series). One LUN per virtual
    disk with array-offloaded snapshots, clones, and online resize.

    ALPHA: not yet validated against a live array or cluster. Lab/test use only
    until verified on real hardware (see docs/INTEGRATION_CHECKLIST.md).

    The repository is named after the Proxmox VE release (PVE_9) rather than the
    Debian base (Debian 13 / Trixie) to avoid confusion.
  </description>
  <person userid="ciriarte" role="maintainer"/>
  <repository name="PVE_9">
    <path project="Debian:13" repository="standard"/>
    <arch>x86_64</arch>
  </repository>
</project>
